00:03:12.439 --> 00:03:15.159
I was the one who cleared things up
with the Time Administration.

00:03:15.159 --> 00:03:17.319
Otherwise, you'd already
have been taken away.

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:19.919
That's why it has to be you.

00:03:20.240 --> 00:03:22.919
