00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:25.199
Who else could handle this?

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:26.039
Market Lord?

00:03:26.120 --> 00:03:27.840
I doubt I can
keep that title much longer.

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:28.800
Find someone else.

00:03:28.800 --> 00:03:29.639
You should go.

00:03:35.039 --> 00:03:36.159
Tell me.

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:39.080
If I really went and found someone else,

00:03:41.560 --> 00:03:43.560
