00:04:28.600 --> 00:04:29.480
Look here.

00:04:29.800 --> 00:04:31.240
This one is contour.

00:04:31.360 --> 00:04:32.319
This one is a highlight.

00:04:33.870 --> 00:04:35.822
These two matte shades are blush,

00:04:35.844 --> 00:04:37.750
and these two shimmery ones
are eyeshadow.

00:04:37.959 --> 00:04:38.639
Got it?

00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:41.959
Aren't these two colors
almost the same?

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:42.519
They are.

00:04:42.519 --> 00:04:43.879
Not even close, okay?

00:04:44.079 --> 00:04:45.279
This one's for the face,

00:04:45.279 --> 00:04:46.560
