00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:52.240
These really look the same, though.

00:04:52.759 --> 00:04:54.399
They're obviously different.

00:04:56.399 --> 00:04:59.399
Never thought that guy
who's usually so clueless

00:04:59.644 --> 00:05:01.120
