00:05:22.519 --> 00:05:23.879
It's just that...

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:25.319
Just what?

00:05:25.560 --> 00:05:26.680
It's just

00:05:27.639 --> 00:05:29.120
even though he's not Ziyi,

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:31.279
he's still my friend.

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:35.319
And once I finish
collecting these artifacts,

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:37.959
