00:09:55.080 --> 00:09:55.919
is me.

00:09:56.039 --> 00:09:56.919
I've got

00:09:56.919 --> 00:09:57.840
your number, too,

00:09:57.960 --> 00:09:59.480
so now we can keep in touch anytime.

