It's too simple for someone like me.

00:10:49.911 --> 00:10:50.960
What's so hard about it?

00:10:51.279 --> 00:10:52.200
There are buttons.

00:10:58.519 --> 00:10:59.279
It shut down.

00:11:02.240 --> 00:11:03.080
It's okay.

